## Publishing

Use `${github_command}` for GitHub publishing only after verifying auth:

```sh
${github_command} auth status
```

Use `${clasp_command}` for Google Apps Script publishing only after verifying
auth and project configuration:

```sh
${clasp_command} ${clasp_auth_check_command}
test -f .clasp.json
```

